2. Rekonstruiraj ipv6 adrese

a) 2001:db8:85a3::1319:8a2e:370:1234
--> 2001:db8:85a3:0000:1319:8a2e:0370:1234

b) 2001::25de:9631
--> 2001:0000:0000:0000:0000:25de:0000:9631

c) 2001::efda:0:9631
--> 2001:0000:0000:0000:efda:0000:0000:9631

d) 2001::efda::9631
--> ne može se riješiti

e) 2001:0:0:efda::9631
-->2001:0000:0000:0000:0000:efda:0000:9631

f) 2001:0:efda::9631
-->2001:0000:0000:0000:efda:0000:0000:9631

g) 2001:efda::9631
-->2001:0000:0000:0000:efda:0000:0000:9631

